(5696, 'en', 'default', '1a5e8350b029491d95ee4ed176e0d985', 'Menus can be displayed in locations defined by your theme, even used in sidebars by adding a &#8220;Custom Menu&#8221; widget on the <a href=\"%1$s\">Widgets</a> screen. If your theme does not support the custom menus feature (the default themes, %2$s and %3$s, do), you can learn about adding this support by following the Documentation link to the side.', NULL, 'LINE', NULL, 0, '', 'c6894d5c5a5eb73410be97f201633a51'),
