(496, 1, '2017-04-24 09:17:20', '2017-04-24 09:17:20', '[vc_row][vc_column el_class=\"fso-animation\"][vc_column_text]\\r\\n<h2>About Ostholt Eventing</h2>\\r\\nSara Algotsson Ostholt, swedish eventing rider with long time experince of horses and a silver medal from the Olympics 2012 in London with her horse Wega. Together with Frank Ostholt, german eventing rider with a gold medal from Olympics 2008 in Peking are the head of Ostholt Eventing. Placed in the town of horses Warendorf, Germany.\\r\\n\\r\\nHere at Ostholt Eventing is it all about the horses. We are breeding for the future, training our horses to reach the top, and nearly every weekend off to eventing competitions with both young and experienced horses. We have also horses for sale, so are you looking for a young horse, experienced horse, show jumping horse, eventing horse or what ever you\'re searching for don\'t hesitate to contact us! Or check out our horses here![/vc_column_text][vc_separator][vc_column_text]\\r\\n<h2>Latest News</h2>\\r\\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_column_text][custom-facebook-feed id=173034462745486 layout=half photosource=photospage loadmore=false num=5 include=media][/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'START', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '60-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-04-24 09:17:20', '2017-04-24 09:17:20', '', 60, 'http://localhost:8888/fso_eventing/2017/04/24/60-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
